  {
    topic: 'Data Lake', difficulty: 'hard',
    q: 'En la arquitectura hexagonal, dónde vive la capa analítica (Bronze/Silver/Gold)?',
    options: [
      'Dentro del dominio, como parte del agregado Order',
      'En la capa de aplicación, como nuevos use cases sobre el agregado',
      'Como puertos y adaptadores separados, suscrita al EventBus existente',
      'En la infraestructura, acoplada al adaptador de base de datos',
    ],
    correct: 2,
    explanation: 'La capa analítica es un suscriptor del EventBus (puerto de salida existente). Tiene sus propios puertos (BronzeEventStore, FactRepository) y adaptadores (InMemory, Postgres, Power BI). El dominio no sabe que existe.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Data Lake', difficulty: 'medium',
    q: 'Qué es una "dimensión compartida" (shared dimension) y por qué no necesita RLS?',
    options: [
      'Una dimensión que existe en todos los tenants -- necesita RLS igualmente',
      'DimDate: los días del año son iguales para todos, no contienen datos de negocio',
      'Una dimensión sin atributos, como un ID suelto',
      'Una dimensión temporal que se borra después de Gold',
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explanation: 'DimDate (year, quarter, month, day_of_week, is_weekend) es idéntica para todos los tenants. No contiene datos de negocio ni información sensible. Todos los tenants comparten la misma tabla de fechas.',
  },
  // ── OBSERVABILIDAD (OTEL) ──────────────────────────────────────
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'easy',
    q: 'Dónde debe vivir la dependencia a @opentelemetry/api?',
    options: [
      'En la entidad Order.ts del dominio',
      'En el use case CreateOrderService.ts',
      'En un adaptador de infraestructura (OtelTracingAdapter)',
      'En el puerto TracingPort',
    ],
    correct: 2,
    explanation: 'OTEL es una librería externa y pertenece a la capa de infraestructura. El adaptador OtelTracingAdapter implementa el puerto TracingPort. Ni el dominio ni los use cases conocen OTEL.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'medium',
    q: 'Qué patrón permite agregar tracing a un use case sin modificarlo?',
    options: [
      'Factory Method',
      'Decorator',
      'Observer',
      'Strategy',
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explanation: 'El Decorator envuelve el use case manteniendo el mismo contrato execute(). withTracing(useCase, port, name) devuelve un objeto que abre span, ejecuta el use case, y cierra span. El use case original no cambia.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'medium',
    q: 'En qué capa se conecta withTracing(useCase, otelAdapter, "CreateOrder")?',
    options: [
      'En el dominio (Order.ts)',
      'En el controller (OrderController.ts)',
      'En la Composition Root (main.ts)',
      'En el test (CreateOrder.test.ts)',
    ],
    correct: 2,
    explanation: 'La Composition Root (main.ts) es donde se instancian todas las dependencias y se conectan los decorators. El controller recibe el use case ya decorado sin saber si tiene tracing o no.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'hard',
    q: 'Cómo se testea un use case decorado con tracing sin un OTEL Collector?',
    options: [
      'Usando jest.mock para mockear @opentelemetry/api',
      'Saltando el test de tracing porque es infraestructura',
      'Usando un FakeTracingAdapter que guarda spans en memoria',
      'Configurando un Collector local en Docker para cada test',
    ],
    correct: 2,
    explanation: 'Un FakeTracingAdapter implementa TracingPort guardando spans en un array. El test verifica spans creados y sus status. Sin mocks, sin Docker, sin OTEL. El puerto hace posible la sustitución.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'hard',
    q: 'Qué principio SOLID justifica que el controller no distinga entre un use case original y uno decorado con tracing?',
    options: [
      'Single Responsibility (SRP)',
      'Open/Closed (OCP)',
      'Liskov Substitution (LSP)',
      'Interface Segregation (ISP)',
    ],
    correct: 2,
    explanation: 'LSP: si el use case decorado implementa el mismo contrato { execute(I): Promise<O> }, puede sustituir al original en cualquier contexto. El controller funciona igual con o sin tracing.',
  },
  {
    topic: 'Observabilidad', difficulty: 'hard',
    q: 'Cuáles son los tres pilares de observabilidad y sus puertos en hexagonal?',
    options: [
      'CPU, RAM, Disco -- MonitoringPort',
      'Traces (TracingPort), Metrics (MetricsPort), Logs (LoggerPort)',
      'Alertas, Dashboards, Runbooks -- AlertPort',
      'Errors, Warnings, Info -- ConsolePort',
    ],
    correct: 1,
    explanation: 'Traces (flujo de requests), Metrics (contadores/histogramas), Logs (eventos estructurados). Cada pilar tiene su puerto y adaptadores: OTEL para prod, fakes para tests, console para dev local.',
  },
];

const topics = [...new Set(questions.map(q => q.topic))];
---

<section id="quiz" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-rose-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Examen</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-3 mb-2">Quiz de Arquitectura Hexagonal</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400">{questions.length} preguntas de opción múltiple. Cada pregunta muestra la explicación al responder.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Config -->
  <div id="quiz-config" class="bg-slate-800/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8">
    <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-6">Configura tu examen</h3>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div>
        <label class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium block mb-3">Tema</label>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" id="quiz-topic-filter">
          <button class="quiz-filter-btn active px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-rose-500/50 bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300 transition-all" data-topic="all">
            Todos los temas
          </button>
          {topics.map(t => (
            <button class="quiz-filter-btn px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/60 text-slate-400 hover:border-slate-500 transition-all" data-topic={t}>
              {t}
            </button>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium block mb-3">Número de preguntas</label>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" id="quiz-count-filter">
          <button class="quiz-count-btn active px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-rose-500/50 bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300" data-count="10">10</button>
          <button class="quiz-count-btn px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/60 text-slate-400 hover:border-slate-500" data-count="20">20</button>
          <button class="quiz-count-btn px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/60 text-slate-400 hover:border-slate-500" data-count="999">Todas</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button id="start-quiz" class="w-full py-3 rounded-xl bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-400 text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors">
      Iniciar examen
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- Quiz in progress -->
  <div id="quiz-game" style="display:none">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 flex-wrap gap-3">
      <span id="quiz-progress" class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono"></span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span id="quiz-score-live" class="text-sm font-mono text-green-400"></span>
        <div class="h-2 w-48 bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
          <div id="quiz-progress-bar" class="h-full bg-rose-500 rounded-full transition-all" style="width:0%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Question card -->
    <div class="bg-slate-800/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span id="quiz-q-topic" class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-rose-500/20 border border-rose-500/30 text-rose-300 font-mono"></span>
        <span id="quiz-q-diff" class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-mono"></span>
      </div>
      <h3 id="quiz-question" class="text-white font-bold text-lg leading-snug mb-8"></h3>
      <div id="quiz-options" class="space-y-3"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Explanation -->
    <div id="quiz-explanation" class="rounded-xl p-5 mb-6" style="display:none">
      <p id="quiz-explanation-text" class="text-sm leading-relaxed"></p>
    </div>

    <button id="quiz-next" class="w-full py-3 rounded-xl bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-400 text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors" style="display:none">
      Siguiente pregunta
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- Results -->
  <div id="quiz-results" style="display:none">
    <div class="bg-slate-800/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center mb-8">
      <div id="result-emoji" class="text-5xl mb-4"></div>
      <h3 id="result-title" class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2"></h3>
      <p id="result-score" class="text-4xl font-mono font-bold mb-4"></p>
      <p id="result-desc" class="text-slate-400 text-sm"></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Breakdown by topic -->
    <div id="result-breakdown" class="mb-8"></div>

    <!-- Wrong answers review -->
    <div id="wrong-answers" class="space-y-4 mb-8"></div>

    <button id="quiz-restart" class="w-full py-3 rounded-xl bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors">
      Volver a intentarlo
    </button>
  </div>
</section>

<script define:vars={{ questions }}>
  var selectedTopic = 'all';
  var selectedCount = 10;
  var quizQuestions = [];
  var currentQ = 0;
  var score = 0;
  var answered = [];

  var diffStyle = {
    easy:   { bg: 'bg-green-900/40 border-green-700/40 text-green-300', label: 'Facil' },
    medium: { bg: 'bg-blue-900/40 border-blue-700/40 text-blue-300',   label: 'Medio' },
    hard:   { bg: 'bg-red-900/40 border-red-700/40 text-red-300',      label: 'Dificil' },
  };

  // ── Config buttons ──
  document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-filter-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      selectedTopic = btn.getAttribute('data-topic');
      document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-filter-btn').forEach(function(b) {
        b.className = 'quiz-filter-btn px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/60 text-slate-400 hover:border-slate-500 transition-all';
      });
      btn.className = 'quiz-filter-btn active px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-rose-500/50 bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300 transition-all';
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-count-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      selectedCount = parseInt(btn.getAttribute('data-count'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-count-btn').forEach(function(b) {
        b.className = 'quiz-count-btn px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/60 text-slate-400 hover:border-slate-500';
      });
      btn.className = 'quiz-count-btn active px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-mono border border-rose-500/50 bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300';
    });
  });

  // ── Start quiz ──
  document.getElementById('start-quiz').addEventListener('click', function() {
    var pool = selectedTopic === 'all' ? questions.slice() : questions.filter(function(q) { return q.topic === selectedTopic; });
    // shuffle
    for (var i = pool.length - 1; i > 0; i--) {
      var j = Math.floor(Math.random() * (i + 1));
      var tmp = pool[i]; pool[i] = pool[j]; pool[j] = tmp;
    }
    quizQuestions = pool.slice(0, Math.min(selectedCount, pool.length));
    currentQ = 0; score = 0; answered = [];
    document.getElementById('quiz-config').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('quiz-results').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('quiz-game').style.display = '';
    renderQuestion();
  });

  function renderQuestion() {
    var q = quizQuestions[currentQ];
    var total = quizQuestions.length;
    document.getElementById('quiz-progress').textContent = 'Pregunta ' + (currentQ + 1) + ' de ' + total;
    document.getElementById('quiz-score-live').textContent = score + '/' + currentQ + ' correctas';
    document.getElementById('quiz-progress-bar').style.width = ((currentQ / total) * 100) + '%';
    document.getElementById('quiz-q-topic').textContent = q.topic;
    var ds = diffStyle[q.difficulty];
    var diff = document.getElementById('quiz-q-diff');
    diff.textContent = ds.label;
    diff.className = 'text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full border font-mono ' + ds.bg;
    document.getElementById('quiz-question').textContent = q.q;
    document.getElementById('quiz-explanation').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('quiz-next').style.display = 'none';

    var optionsEl = document.getElementById('quiz-options');
    optionsEl.innerHTML = '';
    q.options.forEach(function(opt, idx) {
      var btn = document.createElement('button');
      btn.textContent = opt;
      btn.className = 'quiz-option w-full text-left px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-700/50 text-slate-300 text-sm hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all';
      btn.setAttribute('data-idx', idx);
      btn.addEventListener('click', function() { selectAnswer(idx); });
      optionsEl.appendChild(btn);
    });
  }

  function selectAnswer(idx) {
    var q = quizQuestions[currentQ];
    var isCorrect = idx === q.correct;
    if (isCorrect) score++;
    answered.push({ q: q, chosen: idx, correct: isCorrect });

    // Show feedback on buttons
    document.querySelectorAll('.quiz-option').forEach(function(btn) {
      var i = parseInt(btn.getAttribute('data-idx'));
      btn.disabled = true;
      if (i === q.correct) {
        btn.className = 'quiz-option w-full text-left px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border text-sm bg-green-900/40 border-green-500/60 text-green-300';
      } else if (i === idx && !isCorrect) {
        btn.className = 'quiz-option w-full text-left px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border text-sm bg-red-900/40 border-red-500/60 text-red-300';
      } else {
        btn.className = 'quiz-option w-full text-left px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border text-sm border-slate-700 bg-slate-800/30 text-slate-500';
      }
    });

    // Explanation
    var expl = document.getElementById('quiz-explanation');
    expl.style.display = '';
    expl.className = isCorrect
      ? 'rounded-xl p-5 mb-6 bg-green-900/30 border border-green-700/40'
      : 'rounded-xl p-5 mb-6 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-700/40';
    var explText = document.getElementById('quiz-explanation-text');
    explText.className = isCorrect ? 'text-sm leading-relaxed text-green-200' : 'text-sm leading-relaxed text-red-200';
    explText.textContent = (isCorrect ? 'Correcto. ' : 'Incorrecto. ') + q.explanation;

    document.getElementById('quiz-score-live').textContent = score + '/' + (currentQ + 1) + ' correctas';

    var nextBtn = document.getElementById('quiz-next');
    nextBtn.style.display = '';
    nextBtn.textContent = currentQ === quizQuestions.length - 1 ? 'Ver resultados' : 'Siguiente pregunta';
  }

  document.getElementById('quiz-next').addEventListener('click', function() {
    currentQ++;
    if (currentQ >= quizQuestions.length) {
      showResults();
    } else {
      renderQuestion();
    }
  });

  function showResults() {
    document.getElementById('quiz-game').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('quiz-results').style.display = '';

    var total = quizQuestions.length;
    var pct = Math.round((score / total) * 100);

    var emoji = pct >= 90 ? 'Excelente' : pct >= 70 ? 'Bien' : pct >= 50 ? 'En proceso' : 'Sigue prácticando';
    var titleColor = pct >= 70 ? 'text-green-400' : pct >= 50 ? 'text-yellow-400' : 'text-red-400';

    document.getElementById('result-emoji').textContent = pct >= 90 ? '★★★' : pct >= 70 ? '★★' : pct >= 50 ? '★' : '○';
    document.getElementById('result-title').textContent = emoji;
    document.getElementById('result-title').className = 'text-2xl font-bold mb-2 ' + titleColor;
    document.getElementById('result-score').textContent = score + ' / ' + total + ' (' + pct + '%)';
    document.getElementById('result-score').className = 'text-4xl font-mono font-bold mb-4 ' + titleColor;
    document.getElementById('result-desc').textContent = pct >= 90 ? 'Dominas la arquitectura hexagonal.' : pct >= 70 ? 'Buen nivel. Repasa los temas fallados.' : pct >= 50 ? 'Vas por buen camino. Más práctica.' : 'Repasa los conceptos fundamentales.';

    // Breakdown by topic
    var topicMap = {};
    answered.forEach(function(a) {
      var t = a.q.topic;
      if (!topicMap[t]) topicMap[t] = { correct: 0, total: 0 };
      topicMap[t].total++;
      if (a.correct) topicMap[t].correct++;
    });

    var breakdownEl = document.getElementById('result-breakdown');
    breakdownEl.innerHTML = '<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Resultado por tema</h4>';
    Object.keys(topicMap).forEach(function(t) {
      var td = topicMap[t];
      var tpct = Math.round((td.correct / td.total) * 100);
      var barColor = tpct >= 70 ? 'bg-green-500' : tpct >= 50 ? 'bg-yellow-500' : 'bg-red-500';
      breakdownEl.innerHTML += '<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">'
        + '<span class="text-slate-300 text-xs w-36 shrink-0">' + t + '</span>'
        + '<div class="flex-1 h-2 bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">'
        + '<div class="h-full rounded-full ' + barColor + '" style="width:' + tpct + '%"></div></div>'
        + '<span class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-mono w-16 text-right">' + td.correct + '/' + td.total + '</span>'
        + '</div>';
    });

    // Wrong answers
    var wrong = answered.filter(function(a) { return !a.correct; });
    var wrongEl = document.getElementById('wrong-answers');
    if (wrong.length === 0) {
      wrongEl.innerHTML = '';
      return;
    }
    wrongEl.innerHTML = '<h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Preguntas falladas</h4>';
    wrong.forEach(function(a) {
      wrongEl.innerHTML += '<div class="bg-slate-800/60 border border-red-900/40 rounded-xl p-5">'
        + '<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium mb-3">' + a.q.q + '</p>'
        + '<p class="text-red-400 text-xs mb-1">Tu respuesta: ' + a.q.options[a.chosen] + '</p>'
        + '<p class="text-green-400 text-xs mb-3">Correcta: ' + a.q.options[a.q.correct] + '</p>'
        + '<p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed">' + a.q.explanation + '</p>'
        + '</div>';
    });
  }

  document.getElementById('quiz-restart').addEventListener('click', function() {
    document.getElementById('quiz-results').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('quiz-config').style.display = '';
  });
</script>
